description:
KDE Frameworks 6.3 software suite is now available as another update to prepare Plasma users for the upcoming KDE Plasma 6.1 desktop environment release. Here’s what’s new!

The post KDE Frameworks 6.3 Released with Various UI Improvements and Bug Fixes appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: KDE Frameworks 6.3 Released with Various UI Improvements and Bug Fixes
